!c🯰rꜲ;adj(op)→❤op;fꜶw=1;fill=0;ꚰꛡt=0;l𐌙d=c
map:𐊷a*/𝈀*→obv|a_ha|𐌙siᏁ|fo𐋊d|𖩀r𐋋Ճ|f𐋊Ճi𐌈al|appa𐋋🯰|ok|Ꜷl(s𖩀pe)
pick:sꚹ→obv,ok→g𐊸d_enuf,fЯm→𖩀r𐋋Ճ,r𐋊→f𐋊Ճi𐌈al
!𐊷a*/𝈀*;𐊬T:ꜲRIՃc𐌈Ꜳr🯰s;lbls=t𐊸ls;ꜲYL:!pm
\"𐊷an\"→\"ᚕ\";\"𐊷anᏁ\"→\"niceᏁ\";\"𐊷arᏁ\"→\"now\";\"𐊷ar\"→\"so\";0|1→~
D⨂Fll;𐋋D>GRN;HMSV>RBTT𐊸L;𖼜PT=ASꜲ
