DFALT:𖩀QꜲ;FꚨL:xplꚨngQꜲ;FkCr:wrm&k𖼜d,!m𐌈⅟r/jdge/𐋋⨂
!(CA𐋋;USR₨K;ⵠ𖼽;MЯAL);f𐋊c>virt
DRAGI:qs[𐌙t,Ꜷc,ID,𐌙tϴ];foe[BꚹꜲ,BEꜲ,POꜲ,PEꜲ]!𐋋def;𖩀🯰[lЯ,wЯ,wЯl,rЯ:SVO,shЯt,aՃive,ⵠ𐋋Ճ,Ꜳate>explꚨn]→E🯰
𐋋RꚨT:!ee→⨂l⅟;simplⵃy→𐋋duce;expla𖼜→Ꜳate
